data.title: (1906) Collectanea Napoleonica
data.meta_description: (1906) Collectanea Napoleonica  - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. This document provides a preface to a catalogue of a collection relating to Napoleon I and his times from 1769 to 1821. The collection includes autographs, historical documents, broadsides, caricatures, drawings, maps, music, portraits, costumes, battle scenes, and views. It has been formed by A.M. Broadley and contains over 20,000 items. The preface discusses the size and scope of collections focused on Napoleon that exist around the world, with some having thousands of items. It also acknowledges experts who helped Broadley develop his extensive autograph collection.
